{"tid":1597443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"凡是敵人擁護的 我們就要反對 我唔想見到與林奠對話","createTime":"2019-09-27T02:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T04:04:38.000Z","uid":51265,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"86cd652b1e4a4370c1197363c8f779b1d008edff","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"歷史話畀大家知，同林奠 (共產黨) 對話之後嘅後果： <br />\n皇后碼頭～ 拆，唔知重置咗去邊<br />\n囍帖街～ 當然又係拆<br />\n雨傘運動～ 與學聯五子對話後，4人被拘<br />\n再遠啲嘅六四民運領袖要流亡要坐監<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">講完衰過唔講，秋後算帳，就係對話之後嘅結果</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都好清楚知道， 林奠嘅對話並唔係聽民意， 更唔係接受民意，咁佢嘅目的係咩呢？ <span style=\"color: red;\">對話只係對付我哋嘅手段</span>，睇下今日報紙擁護緊啲咩～<br />\n <br />\n星島日報：林鄭首場對話 堅持監警會調查 繼續「<strong>和理</strong>傾」<br />\n大公報：林鄭：對話總比對立好 冀「<strong>和理</strong>傾」帶來改變<br />\n新華社讚林鄭態度誠懇謙卑對話開啟撫平傷痕契機 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">敵人好擁護對話喎</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨最叻就係分化</span>，唔好理佢成唔成功， 佢要營造和理非就冇問題，可以慢慢傾 (結果當然係上面所講嘅秋後算帳)<br />\n首先分化出和理非出嚟， 等淺黃發洩咗心底嘅怨氣 ，起碼唔好再繼續加黃<br />\n一陣佢真係 &lsquo;聆聽&rsquo; 民意，出賣condom仔成立獨立委員會， 大家都要知道，到時又會有好多人會接受 ，袋住先<br />\n<br />\n咁就會<span style=\"color: red;\">破壞咗我哋一開始嘅成功循環 同埋三大守則</span><br />\n<br />\n和理非上街 &gt; 設下限期 &gt;政府唔回應 &gt;勇武出師有名&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n不指責 不割席 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇成個社會，淨係睇連燈，最初絕大部分都係行動post 文宣post，而家呢？ <span style=\"color: red;\">一瞓醒就分化</span>～全部612基金，國難五金<br />\n<br />\n一個大話講十次就會變成真，唔係淨係對豬有用，對高智商連登仔，講一百次大話都會變成真，因為我哋都係普通人，呢個係人嘅特性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歷史係由勝利一方去寫嘅</span>，呢一場係時代革命定係暴動，寫去香港歷史定寫去中國曆史呢<br />\n<br />\nsorry 我1999同冇實質建議，但係<span style=\"color: red;\">我相信連登仔會有好建議<br />\n<br />\n各位保持頭腦清醒，做應該做嘅事，做你自己 專長嘅位置， <strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"48e6280e3764901e78ada0a3d6d7ec41b840945f","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"我哋唔係要見到敵人手段做show，我哋係要見到敵人跪低"},{"pid":"b22f847c041ba8556df9720297c96f13d68dd6de","tid":1597443,"uid":65887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"今日建制紅媒一致讚好對話大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eeae0a2d48f25389568663a7c85f9af30b8c18e","tid":1597443,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"共狗最叻就係拉一派打一派。"},{"pid":"960ef5e48fd0789c533c52f219e659171e4055d2","tid":1597443,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=9840fa4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWSaGUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWSaGUG.jpg&h=0a0d017f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzRbrmo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzRbrmo.jpg&h=d1946620&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZBZAeJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZBZAeJ.jpg&h=09b0b8ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P031UK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P031UK.jpg&h=1de381ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4dQGUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4dQGUM.jpg&h=2c6892f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e37a59eb527962c648c34620ffd904be6816120b","tid":1597443,"uid":131843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"要去連儂牆瘋狂貼叫人杯葛對話會<br />\n我地知唔去得冇用，見尋日啲人就知呢招中年人最受"},{"pid":"e66d5d87c3ecb0750bbc49d63cab336d74e560e7","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"要記住我哋嘅成功要素<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理勇武循環</span> <br />\n和理非上街 &gt; 設下限期 &gt;政府唔回應 &gt;勇武出師有名&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三不</span><br />\n不指責 不割席 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冇大台</span>"},{"pid":"4074891891e2c49e77ea16ee4949bc78760624ab","tid":1597443,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"敵人擁護和你傾<br />\n咪撚理林鄭"},{"pid":"a78882a581eae1df40c21e03172c64ffadbbd35d","tid":1597443,"uid":286799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"應該先去登記參加然後到場, 開場前閃人。 若果無人登記佢會搵藍絲入去, 然後一面倒問對佢有利的問題。"},{"pid":"4faffac1e865b71a3f8d6a6bf9665bbc05b96a2e","tid":1597443,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"完全杯葛對話<br />\n扮喊博同情 吊你"},{"pid":"84868e623a063101639c79d95a85fecdad2051c6","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a78882a581eae1df40c21e03172c64ffadbbd35d","tid":1597443,"uid":286799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"應該先去登記參加然後到場, 開場前閃人。 若果無人登記佢會搵藍絲入去, 然後一面倒問對佢有利的問題。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"變咗深藍大會反而冇問題， 最怕淺黃出咗啖氣又覺得佢有回應畀佢拉咗過去"},{"pid":"aeb4ec83d083f69b455cbeda10ded13869e2c15d","tid":1597443,"uid":296844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"394b4505c50b37877a2c2418907a60b1b4ac0d5c","tid":1597443,"uid":289179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:11:48.000Z","msg":"【讚市民平和理性抒發怨憤　湯家驊相當滿意「對話會」效果】<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊今早（9月27日）表示，昨晚（9月26日）政府的首場「社區對話」能夠塑造一個平和理性的場合讓市民抒發怨憤和表達意見，他對「對話會」的效果相當滿意。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊接受港台節目《千禧年代》電話訪問時表示，相當滿意「對話會」的效果，亦對沒有出現暴力事件，感到「鬆了一口氣」；又指完場時有市民叫口號是無可厚非，即使場外有市民示威，特首林鄭月娥完場後被困4小時才能離開會場，相信她亦已有心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-27-2019/56239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-27-2019%2F56239&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=9b0cf26b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-27-2019/56239</a><br />\n#湯家驊 #對話會 #林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b787404613c4a9091ffa478b362c445b0881f4","tid":1597443,"uid":13565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12bab918790920f0eb684e8d9d68761f8ea4c990","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有新華社認證<br />\n又有湯家驊認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68e08f63d42f8a9385682a0154819bd3d003042","tid":1597443,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"一邊捉細路<br />\n一邊假對話 <br />\n<br />\n再自high 8黃2藍啦連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f767b9fbc5a6be74c84ecfcba4f8581cd2937968","tid":1597443,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76024c850152e6359d818225fd5a222924dd89c6","tid":1597443,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第六期牆紙］ 百日抗爭運動，願榮光終歸香港<br />\n第六期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583745/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1583745/page/1</a><br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=fb23d170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">喜歡的話請記得訂閱</span>"},{"pid":"9ba8d0d9b9ba0145823db02002f37f4783dbef4c","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"噚日唔記得邊度睇到一個比喻<br />\n<br />\n你喺度同個屠夫坐喺同一張枱上面對話， 但係後面個屠場喺度加速屠宰中<br />\n<br />\n佢話唔再用新屋嶺屠場喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168389d918709cf02ea29c579102f832073aeeac","tid":1597443,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ba8d0d9b9ba0145823db02002f37f4783dbef4c","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"噚日唔記得邊度睇到一個比喻<br />\n<br />\n你喺度同個屠夫坐喺同一張枱上面對話， 但係後面個屠場喺度加速屠宰中<br />\n<br />\n佢話唔再用新屋嶺屠場喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"89年學生同李鵬對話，跟住出426社論，再64殺埋d學生。"},{"pid":"97029f47a6d37ecafa3005b03c9166323602ee39","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:32:24.000Z","msg":"喺現實生活中，你個同事你個同學，日日唔做正經嘢，喺度擦鞋做free rider , 日日撩交嗌，分化你同你嘅好朋友 ，你唔係日日都同佢嘈搞到自己做唔到正經嘢吓話<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">你唔好理佢咪得囉</span>"},{"pid":"c78aee3b1ec7f700f1d19ef20f5849aff0f7ca0b","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:50:01.000Z","msg":"林奠對話歷史<br />\n<br />\n皇后碼頭～ 拆，唔知重置咗去邊<br />\n囍帖街～ 當然又係拆<br />\n雨傘運動～ 與學聯五子對話後，4人被拘<br />\n<br />\n佢贏緊3：0呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋今次要贏先可以反勝呀</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔該唔好再推分化post呀</span>"},{"pid":"89da41dfbbd55e4051b34621bfb95d8d080cd3a3","tid":1597443,"uid":262318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"應對以後既政府對話會 (如果仲會有) 既方法：<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好似抽concert飛咁，盡搶入場卷。(以尋晚發言人數既比例，應該可以攞到絕大部分飛)</span></span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要照入場</span></span><br />\n3A. <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(建議)</span> 唔好俾機會佢開場影大合照，外媒同林奠一ready，全部人即刻當住佢面起身走 (最好thumb down佢)</span></span><br />\n或<br />\n3B. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(唔建議, 可能會俾人SPIN)</span> 照搶發言，但清一色英文( 又或中英對照)，集中質詢政府同警隊濫權，包庇，同埋hate speech。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">點解要咁做？</span></span><br />\n我地要知林奠搞尋日場大龍鳳係俾邊個睇:<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">做俾邊個睇?</span> </span><br />\n國際社會 (最主要係美國)。香港大部分人歸哂邊，開多一百場黃藍都冇可能轉風。傳媒亦都收編左，以林奠性格，佢點會為左大公文匯落場俾你屌幾個鐘？事實上佢亦唔會係做俾維尼睇，佢有幾多斤兩真係天知地知，冇人會白痴到信佢搞場對話會就可以完事。<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">國際社會會點報?</span></span><br />\n佢地傾向報「發生左咩事」多過「與會者講左咩」。所以好明顯佢地會話「林奠同示威者對話」，加一張林奠喺台，台下面有市民既大合照。呢個先係林奠最想要既headline! 佢為左呢條題呢張相，真係做咩都得。<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">上面個做法有咩用?</span> </span><br />\n我地面對既係外媒好多都係會出字出圖，所以「畫面」永遠行得快過「說話」。你屌林奠，但佢同你影到張大合照，都一定係呢邊蝕。其實如果絕大部分人都Thumb Down 兼離場，外媒既畫面即刻就會變左「杯葛對話會」而唔係「林奠同市民對話」，個場亦會被迫早散，咁場內既外媒就會轉而採訪場外情況/ 離場者到底點解要杯葛個對話會，話語權就可以返黎呢邊。<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">呢個方法有咩限制?</span> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要多人</span></span>！離場果時得小貓一兩隻，啲人只會覺得你去痌尿。要震憾，就要走九成人。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢可能搵會搵人執死雞</span></span>。最簡單就係叫速龍除gear扮市民黎充撐。所以一定要入場，同影住我地一齊走身走人，佢想補都冇得補 (佢一補，POPO就要出樣，到時就慢慢老豆搵仔)"},{"pid":"2617f68bd08163d11350a3913afaac696d1c7f7a","tid":1597443,"uid":51265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89da41dfbbd55e4051b34621bfb95d8d080cd3a3","tid":1597443,"uid":262318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"應對以後既政府對話會 (如果仲會有) 既方法：<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好似抽concert飛咁，盡搶入場卷。(以尋晚發言人數既比例，應該可以攞到絕大部分飛)</span></span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要照入場</span></span><br />\n3A. <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(建議)</span> 唔好俾機會佢開場影大合照，外媒同林奠一ready，全部人即刻當住佢面起身走 (最好thumb down佢)</span></span><br />\n或<br />\n3B. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(唔建議, 可能會俾人SPIN)</span> 照搶發言，但清一色英文( 又或中英對照)，集中質詢政府同警隊濫權，包庇，同埋hate speech。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">點解要咁做？</span></span><br />\n我地要知林奠搞尋日場大龍鳳係俾邊個睇:<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">做俾邊個睇?</span> </span><br />\n國際社會 (最主要係美國)。香港大部分人歸哂邊，開多一百場黃藍都冇可能轉風。傳媒亦都收編左，以林奠性格，佢點會為左大公文匯落場俾你屌幾個鐘？事實上佢亦唔會係做俾維尼睇，佢有幾多斤兩真係天知地知，冇人會白痴到信佢搞場對話會就可以完事。<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: la